data.description: Welcome home to this adorable property near River Rd. This backyard is calling your friends and family with horse shoe pits, a 7 person hot tub, covered patio and fire pit. Inside you'll find granite counter tops, a high seated bar, SS appliances and a cozy fireplace. Park all your toys under the covered RV parking or the extra deep garage. Motivated seller, bring your offers!
